Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你是神的使者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是从天上掉落下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,人族的孩子身体贫弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我点了篝火给你们暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我们吧  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你在附近有没有看到另一个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一个兽族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只找到你们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我不害怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕自己的救命恩人是很没有礼貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个很奇妙的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫做鲁迪乌斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瑞杰路德·斯佩路迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我坐在你旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请问这里是哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,魔大陆东北方的比耶寇亚地区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来的地方可真遥远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道从这里回中央大陆要多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩为什么会来到这个地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好像被卷入了一场巨大的魔力灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会送你们俩平安回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要是抛下你们不管  有损斯佩路德族的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这份名声早已千疮百孔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝  早上好  这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,斯…斯佩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德  是斯佩路德族!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕我怕我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,基列奴  基列奴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你没有跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  鲁迪乌斯  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起推开了你  对不起要毁约了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是正常人的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是反常的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你很反常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你…你  好…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾…艾莉丝…伯伯…伯雷亚斯…格雷拉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝·伯伯伯雷亚斯·格雷拉特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不对  是「伯雷亚斯」!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瑞杰路德·斯佩路迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只要好好沟通  大家都能做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人总是对我撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么熬夜会被斯佩路德族吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就缩成一团  假装自己睡着了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别当我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你请求的话  瑞杰路德也许会跟你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德  也请你说一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…艾莉丝  请跟我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法  我就当你的朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样  两个人在夜里成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝越来越大胆  有时会说比较冒犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但瑞杰路德听了也不放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁放出「斯佩路德族易怒」这种谎言的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,突然来到一片陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的旅途会很漫长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要把艾莉丝平安送回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,魔大陆  我的冒险要开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你不要动的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你看不到  也知道有魔物呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠着额头上的这颗眼睛看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是经常觉得  要是没这个东西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可以替你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,把它挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她是在开玩笑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有把剑的话  我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能用魔术帮上点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子别操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你待在你哥身边  让他保护你就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是我哥啊?  我才是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的瑞杰路德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已经能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}真可疑!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我不能放那两个人进村子!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你要对孩子弃之不顾吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}他们是陷入灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}才被带来这个地方的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  他们在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人觉得我们可疑  不让我们进村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他会叫村长过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈过之后就可以进村了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他在做心电感应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,米格路德族相互之间离得很远也能交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,米格路德族…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}村长  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}就是这两个孩子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我是鲁迪乌斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}哎呀  真有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还好我有学习魔神语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是村长洛克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的挂坠是在哪里得到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,原来他懂人类语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是师父给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,师父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫做洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛琪希!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛琪希…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛琪希…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}是我女儿的名字!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,原来这是洛琪希老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯  有奇怪的东西在保护田地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看  仔细一看是大龟壳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一个洛琪希  两个洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,三个  四个洛琪希…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要冷静  我的神只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}洛琪希…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我女儿自从离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}已经20多年没听到过消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,20年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}米格路德族的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}究竟有多长呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}如果平安无事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}大概能活上200年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}女儿今年已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}44岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}话说洛琪希现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}真的平安无事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.73,Comment,,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}她在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}她写的信上说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}她在西隆王国…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}过得还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}嗯…  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}她过得好就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,岳父大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要是保罗他们知道我还平安的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许也会哭泣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我们也看到流星向四面八方飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了情况的不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩很亲近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们打算怎么回去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会陪着  不会抛下他们俩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你陪着他们又想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么意图  我只是保护他们平安回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你又进入不了城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能进入城镇?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是碰上意外  我会救这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,即便要杀死所有在场的人  我也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是你  一遇上小孩子就不顾一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你救那个姑娘就是10年前左右的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你这么倔强  能实现你的目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请问他的目标是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德先生的目标是消除斯佩路德族的恶名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这难如登天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,连洛琪希都给了我忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对斯佩路德族的恐惧  在这个世界上已经根深蒂固
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至令艾莉丝那样畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是斯佩路德族在战争中不分敌我的屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是真的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不对!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是拉普拉斯的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拉…拉普拉斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他背叛了我们一族人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以详细说说吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来瑞杰路德说起了历史背后的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  战争中那家伙给了我们一族人长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪是斯佩路德族的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有族人甚至不愿弃之去用别的长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,400年前的战争中  英雄拉普拉斯统一魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也从人族手中赢得了魔族的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族作为属下  与其一同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德所在的族群
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最终接受了拉普拉斯赐予的荣誉长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那些长枪非常厉害  让人觉得战无不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是情况很快不对劲了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉中  我们开始不分敌我地袭击身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有人感到疑惑  没有人注意到变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,后来我们对看到的一切都动了杀心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,最终我们弑亲  弑妻  弑兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,连自己的孩子都不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子用他的生命  将我从诅咒中拯救了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他的灵魂就在这把长枪之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们盲目相信拉普拉斯  收下了诅咒长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而斯佩路德族的恶名  就是对我们的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因此身为战士长的我  有责任恢复一族的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他是不是孤独地度过了400年的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他是否感到遗憾和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,「后悔」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,人族孩子的我  也许能帮你做出一些变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证  我会尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}要走了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}这位是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}是我内人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我叫做洛嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是师父的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你可真年轻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}你真会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我今年已经102岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}那…那还是挺年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}如果你见到洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}告诉她常回家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}岳父大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}我可以这样称呼你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}不开玩笑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}方便的话就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}也请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}谢谢你给我们报了洛琪希的平安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}送给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}非常感谢!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢两位的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnFOT-CinemaCN\pos(640,712)}不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我做下了帮助瑞杰路德的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,前世的我听到他的故事  大概只会一笑了之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是昨晚我决定要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他说的话一下子就打动了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在城镇外受他的保护  在城镇内我会保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,投我以木桃  报之以琼瑶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德先生  今后还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
